title: Qualities of a Good and Bad Friend! Feat. Cayden & Tracy
description:
Hi everyone!

In today's episode, we have not one, but two guests! Cayden and Tracy. We will be talking about how we met, qualities to look for in a friend, and qualities to have and be aware of to be a better friend.

Watch this episode on YouTube: https://youtu.be/4vMzWP63tZk
